#. Tag: title
#: usingtheviews.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Beskrivning"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:3
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Task Editor is a view that displays task data in a tree structure. Most "
"data in the Task Editor can be edited in situ."
msgstr ""
"Aktivitetseditorn är en vy som visar aktivitetsdata i en trädstruktur. "
"Största delen av data i aktivitetseditorn kan redigeras på plats."

#. Tag: title
#: usingtheviews.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigation"
msgstr "Navigering"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can navigate the tree structure using the keyboard:"
msgstr "Du kan navigera igenom trädstrukturen genom att använda tangentbordet:"

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>+</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>+</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand an expandable row."
msgstr "Expandera en expanderbar rad."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>-</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>-</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collapse a collapsible item."
msgstr "Dra ihop ett ihopdragbart objekt."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow left"
msgstr "Vänsterpil"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to previous column in the same row."
msgstr "Gå till föregående kolumn på samma rad."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:53
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow right"
msgstr "Högerpil"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to next column in the same row."
msgstr "Gå till nästa kolumn på samma rad."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:61
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow up"
msgstr "Uppåtpil"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to previous row in the same column."
msgstr "Gå till föregående rad i samma kolumn."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arrow down"
msgstr "Neråtpil"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to next row in the same column."
msgstr "Gå till nästa rad i samma kolumn."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Home"
msgstr "Home"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:80
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to first row, first column."
msgstr "Gå till första raden, första kolumnen."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>End</keycap>"
msgstr "<keycap>End</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to last row, last column."
msgstr "Gå till sista raden, sista kolumnen."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page up"
msgstr "Page up"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to first visible row in the same column."
msgstr "Gå till första synliga rad i samma kolumn."

#. Tag: keycap
#: usingtheviews.docbook:101
#, no-c-format
msgid "Page down"
msgstr "Page down"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to last visible row in the same column."
msgstr "Gå till sista synliga rad i samma kolumn."

#. Tag: title
#: usingtheviews.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Editing data"
msgstr "Redigera data"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Editable items are opened for editing by double-clicking on the item or, if "
"using the keyboard, pressing <keycap>F2</keycap> will open the current item."
msgstr ""
"Redigerbara objekt öppnas för att redigera genom att dubbelklicka på "
"objektet eller, om tangentbordet används, så öppnas det aktuella objektet "
"genom att trycka på <keycap>F2</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When editing an item you can navigate to the next editable item as follows:"
msgstr ""
"När ett objekt redigeras kan du gå till nästa redigerbara objekt på följande "
"sätt:"

#. Tag: keycombo
#: usingtheviews.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Arrow left</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>vänsterpil</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the previous editable item in the same row."
msgstr "Gå till föregående redigerbara objekt på samma rad."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: usingtheviews.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Arrow right</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>högerpil</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next editable item in the same row."
msgstr "Gå till nästa redigerbara objekt på samma rad."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: usingtheviews.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Arrow up</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>uppåtpil</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next editable item in preceding rows."
msgstr "Gå till nästa redigerbara objekt på föregående rader."

#. Tag: keycombo
#: usingtheviews.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>Arrow down</keycap>"
msgstr "&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>neråtpil</keycap>"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid "Go to the next editable item in succeeding rows."
msgstr "Gå till nästa redigerbara objekt på efterföljande rader."

#. Tag: title
#: usingtheviews.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid "Drag &amp; drop and copy/paste"
msgstr "Dra och släpp och kopiera eller klistra in"

#. Tag: para
#: usingtheviews.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Most views support drag &amp; drop and copy/paste. Charts and Gantt charts "
"can be dragged to applications that support images. Table data uses the html "
"mime type, so can be dropped on any applications that supports this. If the "
"view supports moving or copying items internally &eg; the <link linkend="
"\"task-editor\">Task Editor</link>, items can also be moved or copied."
msgstr ""
"De flesta vyer stöder dra och släpp och kopiera eller klistra in. Diagram "
"och GANTT-diagram kan dras till program som stöder bilder. Tabelldata stöder "
"mime-typen HTML, så den kan släppas på vilket program som helst som stöder "
"det. Om vyn stöder att flytta eller kopiera objekt internt, t.ex. <link "
"linkend=\"task-editor\">Aktivitetseditorn</link>, kan också objekt flyttas "
"eller kopieras."
